'From Squeak2.8alpha of 4 February 2000 [latest update: #2210] on 3 June 2000 at 10:15:22 pm'!"Change Set:		119FileDirFix-mdrDate:			1 June 2000Author:			mdr@scn.orgFixes FileDirectory entryAt:ifAbsent: to respect the case insensitivity of some (Windows) native file systems"!!FileDirectory methodsFor: 'file status' stamp: 'sma 6/3/2000 22:11'!entryAt: fileName ifAbsent: aBlock	"Find the entry with local name fileName and answer it.	If not found, answer the result of evaluating aBlock."	| comparisonBlock |	self isCaseSensitive		ifTrue: [comparisonBlock _ [:entry | (entry at: 1) = fileName]]		ifFalse: [comparisonBlock _ [:entry | (entry at: 1) sameAs: fileName]].	^ self entries detect: comparisonBlock ifNone: [aBlock value]! !